{"title":"断臂的维纳斯","uid":"b5fe96d027a7cba0d2691f6775f5aae3","slug":"维纳斯","date":"2021-11-21T08:46:05.000Z","updated":"2021-11-21T09:03:08.767Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/维纳斯.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/11/21/weinasi/weinasi.jpg","content":"<h2 id=\"君子坦荡荡，央视藏鸡鸡\"><a href=\"#君子坦荡荡，央视藏鸡鸡\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"君子坦荡荡，央视藏鸡鸡\"></a>君子坦荡荡，央视藏鸡鸡</h2><h4 id=\"打上马赛克，艺术变三俗\"><a href=\"#打上马赛克，艺术变三俗\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"打上马赛克，艺术变三俗\"></a>打上马赛克，艺术变三俗</h4><p>今天打开豆瓣，封面是断臂的维纳斯，仔细一看，其胸部竟然被打上马赛克。不由得感叹国人是如此纯洁。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/11/21/weinasi/IMG_1035.PNG\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"拓展阅读\"><a href=\"#拓展阅读\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"拓展阅读\"></a>拓展阅读</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width